    "body": "I had a similar problem with this and found it was caused by the initialisation of the hardhat background service. A work around is to move hardhat.config.js or hardhat.config.ts to a different filename temporarily while starting remixd\r\n\r\nPossibly related to: https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/issues/3196",
